VIA ELECTRONIC MAIL
 
February 22, 2008
 
Re: Potential Infringement of Copyrighted Material by www.susanrits.com <http://www.susanrits.com/> 
 
As you are aware, Network Solutions, LLC provides hosting services in connection with your Web site, www.susanrits.com <http://www.susanrits.com/> . We have received a notice from Dan J.
